    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.38.20-21_0001" />
                
                <fw type="curatorial">20</fw>
                <note type="curatorial">Aly Collection</note>
                <note type="clerical">Oct 23 62</note>
                <note type="curatorial">179-4</note>
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>Oct 23, 62</dateline>
                
               
                <salute>Dear Lady:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Just received this. It's the second of the two articles in the Hindustan Times, New Delhi. I'm told it has aroused a lot of interest in a certain group there. There's a possibility I may be invited to talk at several colleges there. If so, I'll apply for a <del/> Fulbright.</p> 
                <closer>
                <salute>Haughtily yourn</salute>
                
                <signed>Dr<hi rend="underline">s.</hi> Neihardt</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <note type="authorial">(over)</note>
                
                <note type="authorial">Should Nicoll be interested in the articles?</note>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.38.20-21_0002"/>
                <fw type="curatorial">2<unclear reason="missing" cert="medium">1</unclear></fw>
                
                <postscript><p><del>I<unclear>have</unclear></del>
                    <lb/>
                I have the original <hi rend="underline">stuff</hi> &amp; <hi rend="underline">photos</hi> in the Hugh Glass monument business of 1923. Also, have stuff &amp; photos <hi rend="underline">re(1)</hi> the unveiling at Lincoln - Will send</p>
                    <closer>
                    <signed>- The Doctors</signed>
                    </closer>
                </postscript>
                
                    <note type="authorial">(1) Footnote - A hard Latin word used for effect.</note> <postscript><p>Are you scared stiff  by the world news? I'm running around shaking and pale as a sheet!</p></postscript>
                    
                  
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
